Query.Title: Daily Foot Traffic In April 2017
Query.Description: This sample query returns daily foot traffic in April 2017 between the hours of 10 AM and 4PM for all properties still owned by Acadia Reality Trust.

Query.Title: Number Of Visitors To Park Meadows Mall
Query.Description: This sample query returns the number of visitors to Park Meadows Mall, Centennial, Colorado on Black Friday for each of the last three years (2017,2018,2019), and how many of those visitors are determined to have come from higher income groups.

Query.Title: Top 20 Census Tracts That Generated Traffic To The Santa Rosa Plaza
